Usage: write_net_groups_topo [-help] [-net_groups <list_of_net_groups>]
                             [-outFile <fileName>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-net_groups <list_of_net_groups>     # To specify netgroups to be added in topo
                                     # file. Default value : *. Example:
                                     # -net_groups {ng1 ng2 ng3-*}
                                     # (string, optional)
-outFile <fileName>                  # busGuide violation log is stored in the
                                     # file specified. Default value :
                                     # bus_guided.topo.v2 (string, optional)